Practice of educational work: viewing and practical experiences in the area of child-rearing activities.Objectives/eesmärkid:  The main aim of the practice is twofold:   (1) to have a preliminary overview about educational work in different types of correctional institutions for children and adolescents, and (2) to have a practical experience working with group of pupils/children at school as an assistant of class teacher.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  Students have got preliminary experience in the area of viewing and identifying upbringing of pupils in educational institutions and are able to connect it with corresponding theoretical background and with self-reflection.
